      "body" : "This appears to be a problem with `bitcoin-cli`, not the RPC server. e.g. `AmountFromValue` calls `value.get_real()` which will raise an exception if the value is not a number.\r\n\r\nBut bitcoin-cli's command line to JSON parsing (`RPCConvertValues`) probably has no proper error handling. If so, I'm surprised this only gets discovered now.",
